This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language understanding and dialogue policy learning in conversational systems. It may also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it proposes an end-to-end deep recurrent neural network for joint learning. Additionally, it may belong to cs.SD (Software Engineering) as it deals with the development of conversational systems, and cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) as it involves human-human dialogues.
